{"type": "article", "id": 23279, "title": "非洲纺织物效果的瓷砖", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-04T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155822IW6dUEVCMJclgqHL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">意大利品牌 Mosaico+ t 最新推出的是 Africa Now 系列，运用了如粉和黑、银和黑搭配的颜色，具有极大的视觉对比，让人想起非洲织物上的图案。在这种颜色搭配的基础上，组合了具有几何感的图案，比如 Pivot 使用边长为 15 毫米的瓷砖，排列出的效果更有冲击力。而 Twist 的宽度有 20 毫米，光泽更低，也更柔和。<a href=\"http://www.mosaicopiu.it/it/articolo/africa-now\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155819Xxo2zcIr68D7YfNA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155820nF4fMqdoRA2Phc8Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155820PiQUv8jtMhRq2u63.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155821cITMJjvX4fgNhSiE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606155821lxhGL1wdao654Hp8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}